{"tid":2167971,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候明白朋友其實唔係咁在乎自己","createTime":"2020-08-21T12:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T15:00:07.000Z","uid":26008,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"89f63deb7dfb697d0a88f7a4ae10459909308452","tid":2167971,"uid":26008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:25:46.000Z","msg":"朋友都係開心時候嘅伙伴姐，其實換上邊個都一樣<br />\n佢哋有比自己更重要嘅人，自己得自己一個<br />\n其實要開始明自己係閒人一個<br />\n佢哋有其他好多嘢喺佢哋嘅生活，我好似得佢哋<br />\n只係我需要佢哋，佢哋其實冇咗我都得"},{"pid":"42f37df1f280904f2edf76fbbe087fd71883cbba","tid":2167971,"uid":90802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:28:26.000Z","msg":"自己永遠都係陪襯 一個視我最重要嘅朋友都冇"},{"pid":"d1f3e2a10ec92a11fac2a7849d2b1f49fa5085df","tid":2167971,"uid":256181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:33:24.000Z","msg":"佢哋就算冇咗我都冇問題，但我冇咗佢地就真係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3289392ceadcf607c64e32217b43c2568f76c973","tid":2167971,"uid":49275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97323fb8b994e93b4cc88e3befb95f44d720b42","tid":2167971,"uid":26008,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"d1f3e2a10ec92a11fac2a7849d2b1f49fa5085df","tid":2167971,"uid":256181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:33:24.000Z","msg":"佢哋就算冇咗我都冇問題，但我冇咗佢地就真係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:35:11.000Z","msg":"佢哋冇咗我生活都多姿多彩，有另一半、返學、返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\